CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 7, 1959, pg. A7 reads: ""Miss Personality" - Dt. Evelyn Burks, seated, won the "Queen for a Day" contest sponsored by Bon Ami Temple 49. She is being crowned "Miss Personality" by her life-long friend, Dt. Sarah Kelly.  Both are members of the Personality Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Evelyn Burks, seated, is crowned "Miss Personality" by Sarah Kelly, posed in domestic interior with small lamp on sideboard, another version
